[4 bladen] [blad 1, recto] Ad [Addendum] 20ff. P.B. II. Witt Library. Seasons: 1) Spring [...] 2) Summer [...]; [blad 1, verso] eingefügt: 1) [Hans Ludwig] Larsen Sale, Parke-Bernet [Galleries], N.Y. 6 Nov. 1947, N° 36 cradled panel 28 1/2 x 41 cm signed at lower left P. BREUGHEL 1624. From P. de Boer, A'dam 1934, N° 2, Exhib. A Thousand Years of Landscape East and West, Boston, Mus. of Fine Arts, 1945, N° 8; [blad 2, recto] Series of the Months. Witt L. [Addendum] 20 ff.[...] Return of Herd, [Bruckman?] 1905, Dark Day [Bruckman?] 1905, Frühlinglandschaft [...]; [blad 3, recto] Winter Witt; To be mentioned in 20 or 25: 1) Grenoble, 30 x 36 painting after Bol's Engraving of Winter; 2) Julius Böhler, Munich signed ! [monogram] 40 x 56 cm; 3) Dora Janssen, Uccle, 'Patinage' 46 x 57 1/2 cm; [blad 4, recto] Landscapes Winter. [Addendum] 20. Hunters in the Snow, Vienna [...]
